{"tid":891094,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國十分一恐怖分子來自伯明翰","createTime":"2018-11-05T23:47:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-06T00:16:20.000Z","uid":117934,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3387ded2f0fd70db15eec2cdc2e2b2dd3a17be7e","tid":891094,"uid":117934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T23:47:32.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】英國國會大樓外恐襲案後，警方在伯明翰等地拘捕8人。本月初有報告指，英國全國有十分之一的恐怖分子來自伯明翰，當地更加被形容是恐怖罪行的溫床。<br />\n<br />\n伯明翰位於西米德蘭茲郡，是繼倫敦後英國第二大城市，人口約為一百一十萬，其中有近兩成二人是穆斯林。<br />\n<br />\n伯明翰東南部的斯帕布魯克地區，是其中一個穆斯林聚居地，佔了區內超過七成人口。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有傳媒指現時每一百五十戶，只有一戶是英國本土白人。</span><br />\n<br />\n有智庫組織本月初發表長達一千頁報告，指英國全國有十分之一的伊斯蘭恐怖分子，均是來自伯明翰五個區域，形容是<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">恐怖罪行的溫床</span>。<br />\n<br />\n據統計，單是斯帕布魯克及周邊地區，過去二十年有26名恐怖分子被定罪，包括現年35歲的哈立德。他原本是克什米爾武裝分子，後來成為阿爾蓋達分支的成員，因為計劃策動比2005年7月英國地鐵和巴士連環爆炸更大規模的炸彈襲擊，哈立德在2013年判監18年。<br />\n<br />\n伯明翰的學校教育亦面臨重大考驗，在校本條例推動<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">多元文化包容</span>背景下，市內多間學校幾年前亦遭伊斯蘭主義入侵，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">企圖讓擁有傳統穆斯林思想的人進入英國教育體系，事件被外界形容為木馬屠城，有傳個別學校更加涉嫌向學生灌輸伊斯蘭極端思想</span>，遭英國政府勒令關閉。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=215203\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D215203&d=Jq7s48F6jj01KZUe6UZzWMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=df74da3a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D215203&h=25f3a81a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=215203</a>"},{"pid":"48392dffe73a470cb2e622428416687695978a34","tid":891094,"uid":80337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T00:11:22.000Z","msg":"係嗰邊讀緊書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56adf6427789b61468eeedfc6a498edfdcdc0a8b","tid":891094,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48392dffe73a470cb2e622428416687695978a34","tid":891094,"uid":80337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T00:11:22.000Z","msg":"係嗰邊讀緊書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T00:13:31.000Z","msg":"巴打小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3c069f280249a39dbdd8c3925bf7b9c7b97290b","tid":891094,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48392dffe73a470cb2e622428416687695978a34","tid":891094,"uid":80337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T00:11:22.000Z","msg":"係嗰邊讀緊書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T00:16:08.000Z","msg":"講少d野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一陣唔知幾句 得罪真主<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23bcb0ca32fe93b3b2ca19b95cb7b8dde21e826f","tid":891094,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T00:16:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係嗰邊讀緊書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>講少d野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一陣唔知邊句 得罪真主<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"}]}